{"tid":619591,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"（認真） 如何定義為‘真香港人’","createTime":"2018-04-06T18:40:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-06T16:22:38.000Z","uid":156233,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"fc7ad237ed5ec2d4d3a191da7df4b1679ee21825","tid":619591,"uid":156233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T18:40:49.000Z","msg":"其實成日話自己係香港人, 但身邊好多朋友都係小學或者幼稚園落黎 都稱自己做香港人  身份證又永遠都係有記號 （R) 話你知你你大陸落黎  噤其實 點先係真係屬於香港人 <br />\n假設：你老豆老母都係大陸出世  落左黎香港生你 噤你係咩人？<br />\n<br />\n噤香港人既定義係跟據咩<br />\n1.身份證 三粒星？<br />\n2.二代或以上 都係香港出世？<br />\n3.講流利廣東話？<br />\n4. 本土意識強？<br />\n仲有冇你地覺得真香港人會有既條件<br />\n<br />\n謝絕小學雞  求認真討論<br />\n<br />\n利申：三代都係香港出世"},{"pid":"71cbee0c75b441354779af0f1912e48745929f75","tid":619591,"uid":126681,"like":57,"dislike":0,"score":57,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T18:44:24.000Z","msg":"要有香港精神 ，見高拜見低踩，憎人富貴厭人貧"},{"pid":"5cf5c80d20a2c8d0ff8088b4d493335266c697f6","tid":619591,"uid":39608,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"quote":{"pid":"71cbee0c75b441354779af0f1912e48745929f75","tid":619591,"uid":126681,"like":57,"dislike":0,"score":57,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T18:44:24.000Z","msg":"要有香港精神 ，見高拜見低踩，憎人富貴厭人貧"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T18:50:07.000Z","msg":"又貪小便宜，有著數要拎盡，炒樓炒iphone炒演唱會飛"},{"pid":"c84187ed75963a1ff0eeae056af00c850fd70e85","tid":619591,"uid":19676,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T18:51:45.000Z","msg":"香港有樓"},{"pid":"4dcacb26e5d4a0e52416a73e43106081b4ef1d40","tid":619591,"uid":156233,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c84187ed75963a1ff0eeae056af00c850fd70e85","tid":619591,"uid":19676,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T18:51:45.000Z","msg":"香港有樓"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T18:57:44.000Z","msg":"噤好多人仲未有 個人認為唔係啦"},{"pid":"06cefbef2f39c4b5d99b9e6085cbea71547dabc3","tid":619591,"uid":96743,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"71cbee0c75b441354779af0f1912e48745929f75","tid":619591,"uid":126681,"like":5